  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy Solitaire is a card game about kitties.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It features classic Solitaire gameplay with thousands of selected deals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a cozy art style and background music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens of adorable kitties accompany you while you play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you get tired, you can interact with the kitties as well.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can happily spend a few hours of leisure time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356790/extras/8215bb2f24ea4f6e5203f74291842a5a.poster.avif?t=1760361174\" width=487 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356790/extras/8215bb2f24ea4f6e5203f74291842a5a.webm?t=1760361174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
